<section id="mission">
  <div class="mission-text">
    <div class="section-tag">Who We Are</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Supercar Club.<br>Networking Org.<br>Media Brand.</h2>
    <div class="accent-divider"></div>
    <p>AYCARS is a supercar networking and events company connecting <strong>supercar owners, entrepreneurs, and high-net-worth individuals</strong> through curated automotive experiences and exclusive social environments.</p>
    <p>We operate across <strong>Dubai and Miami</strong> — hosting events where 40+ exotic cars gather, powerful engines meet powerful minds, and real business relationships are formed.</p>
    <p>AYCARS sits at the intersection of three things: an exclusive supercar club, a high-value networking organisation, and a media brand with hundreds of millions of views. <strong>Cars are our gateway. Relationships are our product.</strong></p>
  </div>
  <div class="mission-image">
